threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered downloader. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis: This PowerPC ELF binary is identified as a downloader or dropper associated with the Mirai botnet. It contains explicit indicators of compromise (IOCs) including hardcoded HTTP GET requests targeting '/bins/mirai.spc', which is a known path used by Mirai-related infrastructure to distribute further malware payloads.
